chen Versuchen, den Holocaust zu verstehen oder dem Antisemitismus zu wehren, runden das Werk ab.   aThe Handbook of Anti-Semitism compiles the present state of knowledge on the phenomenon of Judaeophobia without limits of time or space. The seventh volume includes nearly 700 entries that survey cultural anti-Semitism in film, theater, literature, and the visual arts. It examines the trope of the “Eternal Jew” as well as “Jud Süß;” it shows how novels, films and artwork were used as vehicles for anti-Semitism.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jun 2020) 0aAnti-Jewish filmsxHistoryvHandbooks, manuals, etc. 0aAntisemitism in the pressxHistoryvHandbooks, manuals, etc. 0aAntisemitismxHistoryvHandbooks, manuals, etc. 0aAntisemitismxHistory. 0aAntisemitism. 0aAntisemitisme. 0aAntisemitismus. 4aAnti-Semitism. 4aAntisemitismus. 4aFilm. 4aHandbuch. 4aKunst. 4aLiteratur. 4aTheater. 4aart. 4afilm. 4ahandbook. 4aliterature. 4atheater. 7aHISTORY / Jewish.2bisacsh1 aMihok, Brigitte, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2014z9783110370225oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831103955560 cprintz978311025873840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311034088440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110340884423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110340884.jpg  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2014  aZDB-23-DGGb2014